<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Low Stock Warning</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #FF9800;">⚠️ Low Stock Alert</h1>

        <p>Hi {{storeOwnerName}},</p>

        <p>One of your products is running low on inventory:</p>

        <div style="border: 1px solid #FF9800; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #FFF3E0;">
            <h2 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">{{productName}}</h2>

            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>SKU:</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{productSku}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Category:</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{productCategory}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Current Stock:</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #d32f2f; font-weight: bold;">
                        {{currentStock}} units
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Threshold:</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{stockThreshold}} units</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Recent Sales:</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{recentSales}} units</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Estimated Days:</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0;">~{{estimatedDays}} days</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #d32f2f; font-weight: bold;">
            Action recommended: Restock this product soon to avoid running out!
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{manageInventoryUrl}}"
               style="background-color: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 12px 30px;
                      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
                Manage Inventory
            </a>
        </div>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">

        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;">
            © {{storeName}}. All rights reserved.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
